node.text: We love cooking as a family and letting little Maddox make his own unique concoctions might just be one of my favorite traditions we have together.  It’s messy, fun and a wildly good time!! Love my little chef @maddoxlboss even more when the meals he creates are a hot mess 😂😂😂😂 but while you sit back watching Maddox just be the best haha learn how to make my crab and shrimp bake 😍 #thebosshouse #cookbossstyle #bossstudios

node.text: I had the chance to speak with Dr. Fauci and ask him some questions surrounding the Covid vaccine for not only myself but my daughter. He answered all of my questions and I am so thrilled to share the conversation with you! To learn more about the Covid-19 vaccine, check out #MadeToSave and https://madetosave.org/learn

node.text: We love cooking as a family and letting little Maddox make his own unique concoctions might just be one of my favorite traditions we have together.  It’s messy, fun and a wildly good time!! Love my little chef @maddoxlboss even more when the meals he creates are a hot mess 😂😂😂😂 but while you sit back watching Maddox just be the best haha learn how to make my crab and shrimp bake 😍 #thebosshouse #cookbossstyle #bossstudios
